              AQAMAAAABgABAAAAAQABAA0ADgABAAsAAAAbAAEAAQAAAAMSB7AAAAABAAwAAAAGAAEA
              AAADAAEADwAAAAIAEA==
              """;
  
      @Test
      void reloadsFooClassAndClearsIntrospectionCacheWhenClassLoaderChanges() throws Exception {
